sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as UiImportController / QML
    participant ImportCtrl as ImportController
    participant ImportImpl as IImportStatement (import impl)
    participant Poppler as PopplerService
    participant OpenCv as OpenCvService
    participant Tesseract as TesseractService
    participant Matcher as ActorMatcher
    participant Persistence as AppStateStore

    Note over UI,ImportCtrl: runRoot / runIdPrefix configured by UI/main

    User->>UI: select file / trigger import
    UI->>ImportCtrl: import(type, filePath, runRoot, runIdPrefix)
    ImportCtrl->>ImportImpl: importStatement(ImportRequest)

    ImportImpl->>Poppler: ExtractRequest (pdfPath, outputDir, uniqId)
    Poppler-->>ImportImpl: ExtractResult (RenderedPage[], textElements)

    ImportImpl->>OpenCv: DetectRequest / MaskRequest / CropRequest
    OpenCv-->>ImportImpl: DetectResult / images

    ImportImpl->>Tesseract: ExtractRequest (imagePath, outputDir, uniqId)
    Tesseract-->>ImportImpl: ExtractResult (text, tsv, words, tables)

    ImportImpl->>Matcher: match(text) [per candidate]
    Matcher-->>ImportImpl: ActorMatch (suggested actor/property)

    ImportImpl-->>ImportCtrl: ImportResult (Statement + artifacts)
    ImportCtrl-->>UI: ImportResult

    UI->>User: render review UI with candidates and suggestions
    User->>UI: accept / edit / create actor or property

    UI->>Persistence: request save (AppState / Statement)
    Persistence-->>UI: save result / impact

    Note right of ImportImpl: session artifacts stored under runRoot (rendered images, ocr tsv, extract/candidates.json, metadata)
